title: Petra Cafe
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Located two blocks from the conference center, this small informal cafe, where you order at the counter, offers a number of vegan options. Most vegetarian items are clearly listed, including lentil soup, dolmas (vegetarian grape leaves) and fava beans. Their vegetarian sample plate includes baba ganoush, hummus, dolmas, tabbouleh, falafel, and pita.
